  "title": "智能闹钟功能如何使用？",
  "answer": " <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white\">功能介绍：</p> <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white; orphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\">智能闹钟功能可以设置一个提前提醒时间，如果您在闹钟响铃时间之前的一段时间内，处于浅度睡眠状态，荣耀手环会给您提前的闹钟提醒。如果您处于深度睡眠状态，手环不会打扰您，会在正常的闹钟时间将您叫醒。</p> <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white; orphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\">必要条件：</p> <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white; orphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\">1、确保手环和手机蓝牙连接正常。</p> <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white; orphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\">2、打开华为穿戴APP，点击左上角手环图标，进入智能闹钟菜单，如截图所示进行设置。</p> <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white; orphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\">![http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/4b0be_r0nfn.jpg](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150717160805343001.jpg)  ![http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/4b0bf_cb5pe.jpg](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150717160805830002.jpg)  ![http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/4b0c0_iiydk.jpg](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150717160805466003.jpg)</p> <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white; orphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\">3、设置完智能闹钟以后，从设置页面到主页面，闹钟设置才会生效。 </p> <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white; orphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\">注意：</p> <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white; orphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\">1、如果您设置闹钟的时候，手环和手机蓝牙连接不正常，您的设置信息会在下次手环和手机蓝牙连接正常，重新打开APP同步数据的时候设置生效。</p> <p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:18.0pt;background:white; orphans: auto;widows: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;word-spacing:0px\">2、闹钟功能在关机后可以正常使用，活动提醒功能在关机后无法使用</p>\n",
